Class Room

java.lang.Object
Room
public class Room
extends java.lang.Object
This class is part of the RPandaScape application. RPandaScape is a very simple, text based adventure game. A "Room" represents one location in the scenery of the game. It is connected to other rooms via exits. For each existing exit, the room stores a reference to the neighboring room.
Version:
2021.12.12
Author:
Elie DUBOUX
